Modern Promo – Clean Corporate is an ultramodern and stylish After Effects template with a unique design, colorful and creatively animated shape layers, clean text animations and dynamic transitioning effects. It’s really easy to use and edit with a neat custom controller. A professional looking intro or opener to your business slideshows, promotions, upcoming events, company broadcasts, conferences, commercials and online marketing videos. Impress your business partners with this well organized and creatively animated presentation. No plugins required.

Easy To Use:
Drag & drop your photos or videos, enter text and you’re done.
Modular structure – duplicate, remove, or rearrange scenes as you want.
Well organized template – user-friendly interface.
Media placeholder: 20 (you can add an infinite number of holders).
Text placeholders: 10 (you can add an infinite number of holders).
Materials:
Photos and videos are not included.
Music is not included. I’ve used in the preview:
Technology Corporation

